This directory contains some AVR firmware code:

main stuff (see READMEs in those dirs):
    bootloader/ - ACRIS bootloader 
    ledctrlr    - main LED controller firmware

other stuff:
    combine.sh  - combine bootloader hex file with application hex file for
                  combined programming
    boardtest/  - simple bring-up test that lets you flash some LEDs and stuff
    huecycle/   - onboard color calculation (never tested)
